stateDiagram-v2
  %% Authored stress fixture (Mermaid@11.12.2)
  %% Focus: choice + fork/join + notes + markdown in edge labels.

  [*] --> Init
  Init --> if_state: _check_

  state if_state <<choice>>
  if_state --> Fork: **yes**
  if_state --> Fail: **no**

  note right of if_state
    Decision point.
    Multiple lines.
  end note

  state Fork <<fork>>
  Fork --> WorkA
  Fork --> WorkB

  WorkA --> Join
  WorkB --> Join

  state Join <<join>>
  Join --> Done: _merge_

  Fail --> [*]
  Done --> [*]

